」（Beacon）轉發「飛機守望」（Aircraft Spots）公布的較完整的MQ-4C飛行路線圖，該軍機從美屬關島安德森空軍基地出發，接近廣東領海基線後並沒有馬上返航，而是轉向東南一路貼著基線飛行，直到飛越海南省南方之後才轉向南海。"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"軍方今早在蘋果A1 頭版發現美軍機進入領空"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfff860ac97bbfaf04a1ca3b0ac92a75c25b7fa8","tid":2344934,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"犯我大共者， 雖千里外，必誅之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6d468d623d002e589926c26c57dbb29d4501b5","tid":2344934,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:05:24.000Z","msg":"下次攞埋 ninja missile"},{"pid":"7f332be744b31d1e2557b0813eef0c031fef441c","tid":2344934,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"攔截信息 偵測 反潛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b287be05c98f3cc0cd446f37e367b8491c6e7d3","tid":2344934,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:13:02.000Z","msg":"有冇順便斬埋首呀？反正順路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00baf83327f4956c271bb5b55e53b1c054f47730","tid":2344934,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:15:06.000Z","msg":"係邊個twitter account"},{"pid":"56815c296cfb0d19ea15e88aa2be9df394c1a34e","tid":2344934,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"打啦你地.jpg"},{"pid":"46160e7a73b31f65f2ccd7a333543dd0b65b031e","tid":2344934,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"共機繞台 &gt; 台灣戰機升空攔截<br />\n美軍戰機繞支 &gt; 共媒：我睇到 我